Notices Logic

start
	page loads
	no checkboxes checked - all categores assumed
	loop pulls out all cats
	provides correct pagination (posts per page = 10)
end

start
	page loads
	no checkboxes checked - all categores assumed
	loop pulls out all cats
	provides correct pagination (posts per page = 10)
	category one checked
	erase all posts (AJAX)
	loop pulls out cat 1 posts
	provides correct pagination (posts per page = 10)
end

start
	page loads
	no checkboxes checked - all categores assumed
	loop pulls out all cats
	provides correct pagination
	cat 1 checked
	jquery script submits to server php for checked box
	page refreshes
	loop pulls only cat 1 posts
	provides correct pagination (posts per page = 10)
end